{"tid":1047134,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"就得人嘅女仔 根本一啲都唔charming","createTime":"2019-03-04T17:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T13:29:06.000Z","uid":104086,"like":339,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"056b4d083e260985c9ec73bfb153c66b0ee34e8d","tid":1047134,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:27:08.000Z","msg":"拍過幾次拖 幾次男仔一開始都覺得我好就得佢 唔洗下下港女咁就住 <br />\n我成日都冇乜所謂 少少野有乜好爭 <br />\n只要佢鐘意我就下佢有咩所謂<br />\n<br />\n但到最後 佢地都利用我所謂嘅「就得人」<br />\n變本加厲去發脾氣 發忟憎 甚至呃我 <br />\n<br />\n根本男人都係鐘意啲控制唔到嘅女人<br />\n你千依百順只會覺得你一啲挑戰性都冇 <br />\n哈"},{"pid":"81f8da8e635681f186cd5338f3dd8c0d4ebdd57f","tid":1047134,"uid":136186,"like":111,"dislike":17,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"你唔識睇人 完"},{"pid":"f88f34bff25f482802a339042b3f786cdc9b6bae","tid":1047134,"uid":210414,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"a2b5dfaafbf871d5fda174e763425353e38e4240","tid":1047134,"uid":104086,"like":106,"dislike":8,"score":98,"quote":{"pid":"81f8da8e635681f186cd5338f3dd8c0d4ebdd57f","tid":1047134,"uid":136186,"like":111,"dislike":17,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"你唔識睇人 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"點先為止識睇？<br />\n個個男人一開始都做到天上有地下無咁好架啦<br />\n拍拖一年咪之後變晒"},{"pid":"0da44547ebb7d298cac375a2bcebfbf71a756d01","tid":1047134,"uid":160584,"like":102,"dislike":1,"score":101,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"以為自己開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開始就唔港女 唔發脾氣<br />\naa下就變到我比70%<br />\n做錯小小野 遲幾分鐘就俾人屌上天花<br />\n佢講過唔算數 我唔發脾氣 佢就獲獲都講完就算 好心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a553cd7470a2953680d86e493d74c498c1